PNG files placed in this folder will be used as the App Fair preview screenshots.

The files should be named according to the following pattern:

  `screenshot_NUMBER-PLATFORM-MODE-WIDTHxHEIGHT@SCALEx.png`

For example:

  * screenshot_01-mac-dark-1024x768@1x.png
  * screenshot_01-mac-light-1024x768@1x.png
  * screenshot_02-iphone-dark-1284x2778.png
  * screenshot_03-iphone-dark-2778x1284.png
  * screenshot_04-ipad-dark-2224x1668.png
  * screenshot_04-ipad-light-2224x1668.png

